## {title:} ##

_30 Sep -- 02 Oct 2011, Baarlo, NL_

[ProgPower Europe](http://www.progpowereurope.com) is a progressive metal festival in the Dutch village of Baarlo (Limburg) with a wide variety of upcoming and established bands in the genre. ProgPower is not only known for its interesting music, but also for its unique atmosphere. It’s no surprise that ProgPower has many regular visitors who celebrate progressive metal in Baarlo every year.

